{"title":"计蒜客-找数字","uid":"8e7684e013c6a1b3dbe92725121f630f","slug":"计蒜客-找数字","date":"2021-07-31T06:19:00.000Z","updated":"2021-08-01T08:52:45.305Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/计蒜客-找数字.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>补充练习</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h3 id=\"题意概括\"><a href=\"#题意概括\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题意概括\"></a>题意概括</h3><p>给一个数 <em>n</em>，让你找出一个只由 0,1 组成的十进制数 <em>m</em>，要求这个正整数 <em>m</em> 可以被 <em>n</em> 整除。</p>\n<h3 id=\"题目分析\"><a href=\"#题目分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目分析\"></a>题目分析</h3><p>搜索裸题，设置上界，每次在末尾添加一个0或1，直到满足题意为止。</p>\n<h3 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">#include &lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;\n#define int long long\nusing namespace std;\n\nint read() {\n\tchar c = getchar();\n\tint f = 1, _ = 0;\n\twhile (c &gt; '9' || c &lt; '0')\n\t\tf = (c == '-') ? -1 : 1, c = getchar();\n\twhile (c &lt;= '9' &amp;&amp; c &gt;= '0')\n\t\t_ = (_ &lt;&lt; 3) + (_ &lt;&lt; 1) + (c ^ 48), c = getchar();\n\treturn _ * f;\n}\nint n, ans;\n\nint dfs(int now) {\n\t//cout &lt;&lt; \"now:\" &lt;&lt; now &lt;&lt; endl;\n\tif (now &gt; 100000000000)\n\t\treturn 0;\n\tif (now % n == 0 &amp;&amp; now != 0) {\n\t\tans = now;\n\t\treturn 1;\n\t} else if (now * 10 &lt; 1e19) {\n\t\tif (dfs(now * 10 + 1))\n\t\t\treturn 1;\n\t\tif (dfs(now * 10))\n\t\t\treturn 1;\n\t}\n\treturn 0;\n}\n\nsigned main() {\n\tn = read();\n\tdfs(0);\n\tcout &lt;&lt; ans &lt;&lt; endl;\n\treturn 0;\n}</code></pre>\n\n","text":"补充练习 题意概括给一个数 n，让你找出一个只由 0,1 组成的十进制数 m，要求这个正整数 m 可以被 n 整除。 题目分析搜索裸题，设置上界，每次在末尾添加一个0或1，直到满足题意为止。 代码#include &lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt; #define int...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":829,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"题解","slug":"题解","count":33,"path":"api/categories/题解.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"恢复OI实力","slug":"恢复OI实力","count":23,"path":"api/tags/恢复OI实力.json"},{"name":"搜索","slug":"搜索","count"